new file mode 100644
index 0000000..a91ce86
--- /dev/null
+++ b/runbooks/P56_AUDIT_CHAIN.md
@@ -0,0 +1,30 @@
+# P5.6 Audit-chain hardening
+
+## What this layer adds
+- `scripts/check_execution_audit_chain.py` — read-only DB checker + JSON/textfile exporter
+- `runbooks/server/runbook_server.py` — `/api/audit-chain/latest` endpoint with filters by `sid`, `signal_id`, `closed_trade_id`, `kind`
+- `monitoring/prometheus_rules_execution_p56_audit_chain.yml` — stale/broken-chain alerts
+- `monitoring/grafana/dashboards/trade_execution_p56_audit_chain_health.json` — overview dashboard
+
+## Execution
+```bash
+python3 scripts/check_execution_audit_chain.py \
+  --dsn "$EXECUTION_AUDIT_CHAIN_DSN" \
+  --report-path ./latest_execution_audit_chain.json \
+  --textfile-path ./latest_execution_audit_chain.prom
+```
+
+## Runbook endpoint
+- `GET /api/audit-chain/latest`
+- filters:
+  - `sid`
+  - `signal_id`
+  - `closed_trade_id`
+  - `kind`
+  - `limit`
+
+## Investigation flow
+1. Alert fires from Prometheus rule.
+2. Open `/api/audit-chain/latest`.
+3. Narrow by `sid`, `signal_id` or `closed_trade_id`.
+4. Backfill or repair upstream writer only after verifying the missing link kind.

